init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Well, I'm here to tell you that it is possible.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: What does it mean to live before?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm literally thinking these thoughts, and yet there is no time or space to accommodate this reality.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think I'll stay here a bit longer and let it sink in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Or, if not, I'll accept that those questions may never be answered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My life is finished, but I am here.
